# RELEASE GOAL

Atlas Version 1.0 should allow a founder to:

✓ Create an invention.

✓ Upload supporting documents.

✓ Allow Atlas to perform autonomous analysis.

✓ Coordinate AI departments.

✓ Generate engineering specifications.

✓ Generate patent research.

✓ Generate manufacturing preparation.

✓ Produce investor-ready materials.

✓ Produce business deliverables.

✓ Maintain complete project history.

✓ Coordinate work automatically.

✓ Escalate only meaningful approval decisions.

without requiring the founder to manually manage workflows.

====================================================================
# DEVELOPMENT PHILOSOPHY

Development currently prioritizes autonomous capability over interface
refinement.

Priority Order:

1. Autonomous execution

2. Engineering intelligence

3. Native CAD foundation

4. Manufacturing intelligence

5. Patent intelligence

6. Market intelligence

7. Financial intelligence

8. Investor intelligence

9. Launch intelligence

10. Founder Experience polish

UI improvements remain intentionally deferred until Atlas is capable of
performing the majority of inventor work autonomously.

