# RELEASE BLOCKERS

Current Critical Blockers

• Native Engineering Intelligence not yet complete.

• Native CAD architecture not yet implemented.

• Manufacturing intelligence pipeline not yet complete.

• Full Patent Intelligence reasoning engine not yet complete.

• Continuous Market Intelligence not yet complete.

• Autonomous company behavior not yet complete.

No cosmetic or UI issues are considered release blockers while the
autonomous operating system remains under active development.

====================================================================
```
====================================================================
# KNOWN ISSUES

The following items have been intentionally deferred until the
autonomous operating system reaches architectural completion.

These are NOT considered release blockers at this stage.

------------------------------------------------------------
Founder Experience

• Too much explanatory text throughout workspaces.

• Important information is buried beneath repeated descriptions.

• Users should receive concise executive summaries first.

------------------------------------------------------------
Workspace Design

• Some workspaces still feel document-oriented rather than
operating-system-oriented.

• Several pages expose internal execution details that should eventually
be collapsed behind "View Details."

------------------------------------------------------------
Execution Center

• Execution records can appear repetitive during long-running workflows.

• Founder-facing execution summaries should eventually replace verbose
execution logs.

------------------------------------------------------------
Packages

• Package descriptions are repetitive.

• Future redesign should emphasize package readiness and outputs instead
of instructional text.

------------------------------------------------------------
Department Pages

• Department pages currently explain too much.

Future redesign goals:

✓ Show current status.

✓ Show next action.

✓ Show estimated completion.

✓ Hide secondary details unless requested.

------------------------------------------------------------
Founder Dashboard

Long-term vision:

The CEO Command Center becomes the primary Atlas experience.

Departments become supporting workspaces rather than primary navigation.

====================================================================
