4. Preserve all existing architecture.

5. Run the complete validation pipeline before deployment.

6. Update this master plan after successful completion.

====================================================================
# FINAL OBJECTIVE

Atlas Version 1.0 is complete when it functions as a true autonomous
company for inventors.

The founder should be able to present an invention once, after which
Atlas autonomously coordinates every participating department,
continuously advances the invention, keeps all knowledge synchronized,
and requests founder input only when legally, strategically, or
commercially necessary.

Success is measured not by the number of reports generated, but by
Atlas' ability to independently execute meaningful work, make informed
recommendations, and guide an invention from idea to commercialization
through a unified, explainable, and trustworthy operating system.

